OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud, haar and a spot of
OL,6,Fdrizzle across Shetland in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Cloudy soon clearing for
OL,8,FOrkney, then a bright morning with
OL,9,Fsome sunny spells. Then cloud and
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain spread northeast
OL,11,Fthrough the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe evening and overnight with further
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain, turning heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes and perhaps quite persistent for
OL,17,FOrkney later. Some haar patches around.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
