OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLargely cloudy throughout the
OL,6,Fday with some haar and outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, occasionally heavy and perhaps
OL,8,Fquite persistent for a time in the
OL,9,Fmorning. Becoming generally drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,13,Fdry on Monday with some bright spells
OL,14,Fbetween areas of low cloud. Cloudy on
OL,15,FTuesday and Wednesday with occasional
OL,16,Frain. Mainly light winds. Areas of
OL,17,Fhaar at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
